(114, '我正在嘉兴我弟弟这里，不久前他和对象分手了，现在他睡下了，每天早早地起床然后跑步。\r\nI am in JiaXing where my brother lives, he broke up with girl friend not long ago, now he is sleeping.  Everyday he wakes up early and take a walk.', '2016-08-19 16:33:06', 'words'),
(115, '做了一个梦，有地铁、大深坑和死亡。让我想到了爱因斯坦那句话，没有想象力的灵魂就像是没有望远镜的天文台。想到跟《三体》中小说的氛围竟还有点契合。我要持续不断的努力才行。\r\nI had a dream, about metro、a huge deep hole and death. Reminds me one word said by Einstein ---- No imagination a soul, as no telescope a observatory. The atmosphere correspond to《THR THREE-BODY PROBLEM》one. I think I must stick to my struggle!', '2016-08-19 16:35:59', 'words'),
