(146, 'A footer typically contains information about the author of the section, copyright data or links to related documents.一个<a href="javascript:void(0);" class="tag">&lt;footer&gt;<a>一般用来提供节段作者的信息、版权数据或者相关文档的链接。<a href="javascript:void(0);" class="tag">#HTML5</a>', '2016-08-21 00:21:34', 'words'),
(147, 'This(&lt;article&gt;) could be a forum post, a magazine or newspaper article, a blog entry, an object, or any other independent item of content. <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="tag">&lt;article&gt;</a>可以表示这个论坛帖子、杂志或者报纸的文章、一篇博客、一个对象或者其它独立的内容项。typically by including a heading (&lt;h1&gt;-&lt;h6&gt; element) as a child of the &lt;article&gt; element.它通常包含一个标题标签，作为自己的子元素。', '2016-08-21 00:32:24', 'words'),
